# ArcGIS Location Platform API key, used for the Esri "topographic" basemap in
# StoryMap. Get one (free) at https://location.arcgis.com and restrict it by
# referrer (e.g. raluca-nicola.net, localhost) in the dashboard.
# PUBLIC_ vars are exposed to the client, which is expected for basemap requests.
# Copy this file to `.env` and paste your key. Without it, StoryMap falls back to
# the CARTO Voyager basemap.
PUBLIC_ARCGIS_API_KEY=
